@META
dir: src/components
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 4
stack: React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion

@EXPORTS
providers.tsx: Providers — wraps app with SessionProvider & QueryClientProvider & Toaster
auth-provider.tsx: AuthProvider — manages auth session & syncs with user store
ErrorBoundary.tsx: ErrorBoundary — React error boundary with fallback UI

@FUNCTIONS
Providers({children}) → JSX
  purpose: root provider tree: NextAuth SessionProvider + TanStack QueryClientProvider + react-hot-toast Toaster
  side-effects: none
  called-by: src/app/layout.tsx

AuthProvider({children}) → JSX
  purpose: sync NextAuth session with Zustand user store on mount
  side-effects: cache (user store sync)
  called-by: Providers component

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: ui/, layout/, chapters/, certificate/, cognitive-glitch/, onboarding/, profile/, skills/, tests/
external: next-auth/react, @tanstack/react-query, react-hot-toast, react

@STANDARDS
- Sub-directories organize by feature domain
- ui/ = design system primitives (reusable across app)
- layout/ = structural components (navigation, page layout, grid system)
- chapters/ = chapter-specific components
- Other dirs = feature-specific components
